상품별 검사항목 구성. 검진 상품(HC_CHECKUP_PRODUCT)에 어떤 검사항목(TEST_ITEM_CD)이 포함되는지. 복합 PK: CHECKUP_PRODUCT_NO + PARTNER_CENTER_ID + TEST_ITEM_CD + CHOICE_GROUP_NO

**HC_PRODUCT_TEST_ITEM**
CHECKUP_PRODUCT_NO:int PRI NN
PARTNER_CENTER_ID:char(6) PRI NN
TEST_ITEM_CD:varchar(20) PRI NN
CHOICE_GROUP_NO:int PRI NN
CHOICE_COUNT:int
PRODUCT_PROPOS_TYPE:char(2)
REG_DT:char(14)
ONPAY_AMOUNT:int
NHIS_CHECKUP_YN:char(2)
PROPOS_DESC:varchar(2000)
BUNDLE_CHOICE_COUNT:int
CHOICE_BUNDLE_NO:int NN
CHOICE_GROUP_BUNDLE_NO:int def=0
MIG_YN:char(1) MUL
MIG_DT:char(8)
MIG_PKG_CD:varchar(100)
PKG_CD:varchar(20)
TOP_DISPLAY_YN:char(1)

